ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT Anguilla FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authroizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Governement of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of Anguilla under entrustment from the Government of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
